title: Lobo's Mixed Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Fast food, Take-out, Tex-Mex, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A fast food burgers and wraps place that has several lacto-vegetarian items. You can get a Morningstar brand veggie pattie or veggie chicken on your burger. Vegans need to ask to omit cheese/dairy. Its website states "It probably won't kill you."
